        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/onlysunshine18/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1984058-6.jpg" alt="陪戎校尉" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27760762/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27760762/" class="">第301页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/onlysunshine18/" class=" " title="陪戎校尉">陪戎校尉</a>
                (一生俯首拜阳明)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27760762">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27760762/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p27760762-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">作者准确的语言到了中国未来发展的趋势阶段，现在中国就处在第三阶段，能否平稳发展到第四阶段，并且避免动乱与分裂，这是一个大问题，愿佛祖保佑我大中华走出现在的阴霾。


 </span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-07-25 09:42</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                作者准确的语言到了中国未来发展的趋势阶段，现在中国就处在第三阶段，能否平稳发展到第四阶段，并且避免动乱与分裂，这是一个大问题，愿佛祖保佑我大中华走出现在的阴霾。
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p27760762-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p27760762-2.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p27760762-3.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







